# Insights

## Source of truth

- Grain / credit / fact contract: `docs/Database_Outline.md` (Insights / grain sections)
- Product priority & phases: `docs/Status.md`, `docs/Analytics_Overhaul_Proposal.md`
- Implementation: `src/lib/insights.ts`, `src/screens/insights/`

## Locked model (Phase 1a)

- **Source:** `v_log_set_facts` (canonical `time_seconds` / `distance_meters` / `tonnage` / `effective_reps`).
- **Lens** = group-by grain (PG / category / muscle / session / block / sequence label).
- **Metric** = Reps | Time | Distance | Tonnage | Sets | **Auto** (per-bucket heuristic: distance → time → reps). Never sum mixed metrics.
- **Filters** = sheet (session / block label, set type, Variations, Tools); dates use real pickers (default last **7** days inclusive).
- **Set type:** Working-only default + include-warmups toggle.
- **Credit-each** for multi-tag grains (PG / category / muscle). Honest partition for nest labels + once-totals.
- **Balance:** category enum, **data-only** (hide zeros).
- **Complete logs only.**

## Phase 1b (not yet)

- Persist PG **Counts as** (`natural_metric`) + balance group; Insights Auto reads settings. See proposal § "PG Counts as (Phase 1b)".

## Do not

- Ship Power cube, credit weights, full PG-groups enum replacement, or Chat 6 seed dump from Insights polish chats.
